headline: PepsiCo Announces Timing and Availability of Third-Quarter 2025 Financial Results
summary: PepsiCo, Inc. (NASDAQ: PEP) today announced that it will issue its third-quarter 2025 (ending September 6) financial results and other related information on Thursday, October 9, 2025 by posting the following materials and links on the company's website at www.pepsico.com/investors.
